frc.team670.robot.subsystems

Class Arm

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.team670.robot.subsystems.Arm

  • public class Arm
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores possible arm states. Does arm-related math Represents the arm mechanism on the robot. Link to a model of the arm: https://a360.co/2TLH2NO
    Author:
    shaylandias, ctchen, rghosh670
